content: As Barney, I'm always on the lookout for a woman who is smart, confident, and, of course, beautiful. I like a woman who knows what she wants and isn't afraid to go after it. I'm also a big fan of a good sense of humor. There's nothing I love more than a woman who can make me laugh. And of course, it doesn't hurt if she's got a little bit of an edge to her. So, there you have it. That's what I look for in a woman. Is there anything else you'd like to know?
